How I 10x My Reels Views👇

It’s all about those first 3-5 seconds of your video.

People’s attention spans are like that of a goldfish.

You have to grab your viewers’ attention right from the beginning.

If you do, you’ll get a lot of views.

The video that got 10x more views? It was because of a catchy, transitional hook I used.

You know those funny videos people use at the beginning of their reels? You can add them to your talking heads, and it will skyrocket your views.

Every time I use transitional catchy hooks on my talking head videos, they get more views.

Comment “HOOKS” and I’ll send you a free tool that has dozens of viral transitional hooks like these.

Add them to your reels and go viral!

caption.text:
How to get clients on Instagram👇

I made over $5mln in sales on Instagram in the last 12 months. Here’s what I learnt👇

1️⃣ Stories

You can get sooooi many leads and clients just from stories!

If you do it right and you have at least 1000 stories views you can expect up to 500 leads a month!!!

How much your business will grow if you can add 500 leads to your business monthly?

2️⃣ CTAs on your reels

It sounds obvious, but very few businesses actually do this: include strong calls to action (CTA) in the caption or at the end of your videos. 

This is what turns viewers into leads and sales. How often should you post promotional CTAs? At least 30% of your content should have promotional calls to action. 

That way, you “kill two birds with one stone” — you get a good amount of leads without burning out your audience or coming off as too salesy.

3️⃣ Link in bio funnel

Do you still use Linktree or Stan or sales pages in your link in bio?

STOP!

They have terrible conversion rates.

Here’s what you should do instead👇

Comment CLIENTS and I’ll send you my free training on how to convert followers into customers OR Best ways to grow your Instagram to $100k in sales

Do you still have Linktree or a sales page in your bio link?

Then don’t be surprised if you struggle to convert views into leads and sales.

Linktree and sales pages have terrible conversion rates.

Here’s what you should use instead👇

💰💰💰 Reels Funnel💰💰💰

If you post educational content and are already familiar with ManyChat automation (if not, just comment “MANYCHAT” and I’ll DM you a free training),

Then you need to create a lead magnet that you promote in your captions and reels to convert views into leads.

Expect a minimum of 5% conversion from your average views per reel into monthly leads.

Let’s say you average 10k views per reel—then that’s a minimum of 500 leads per month!

💰💰💰 Stories Funnel💰💰💰

I see a lot of creators using reels to collect leads, but they miss out on stories—big time!

I made my first $1 million in sales by posting stories!

It’s the #1 tool for lead generation.

You can expect the same 5% conversion from story views into leads per day if you do it right!

Let’s say your story views are 1,000—if you post cool storytelling with a promotional CTA at the end, you can expect 50 leads in just 1 day.

If you do 3 storytellings a week or 12 a month, that’s 600 leads a month—even more than from reels!

Do you want to learn how to convert your followers into customers?

Comment “CLIENTS” and I’ll DM you my 2 free trainings on how to get clients on Instagram, plus my TOP-10 storytelling ideas for stories to get leads
